001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 13,
011    displayName = "Time Change",
012    usedByTidepool = true
013)
014public class TimeChangedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    private long timePrior;
017    private long timeAfter;
018    private long rawRTC;
019    
020    public TimeChangedHistoryLog() {}
021    public TimeChangedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long timePrior, long timeAfter, long rawRTC) {
022        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
023        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, timePrior, timeAfter, rawRTC);
024        this.timePrior = timePrior;
025        this.timeAfter = timeAfter;
026        this.rawRTC = rawRTC;
027        
028    }
029
030    public TimeChangedHistoryLog(long timePrior, long timeAfter, long rawRTC) {
031        this(0, 0, timePrior, timeAfter, rawRTC);
032    }
033
034    public int typeId() {
035        return 13;
036    }
037
038    /**
039     * <table border="1">
040     * <caption>Parsed fields for TimeChangedHistoryLog:</caption>
041     * <tr><td><code>timePrior</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
042     * <tr><td><code>timeAfter</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
043     * <tr><td><code>rawRTC</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
044     * </table>
045     */
046    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
047        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
048        this.cargo = raw;
049        parseBase(raw);
050        this.timePrior = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10);
051        this.timeAfter = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14);
052        this.rawRTC = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
053        
054    }
055
056    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long timePrior, long timeAfter, long rawRTC) {
057        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
058            new byte[]{13, 0},
059            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
060            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
061            Bytes.toUint32(timePrior), 
062            Bytes.toUint32(timeAfter), 
063            Bytes.toUint32(rawRTC)));
064    }
065    public long getTimePrior() {
066        return timePrior;
067    }
068    public long getTimeAfter() {
069        return timeAfter;
070    }
071    public long getRawRTC() {
072        return rawRTC;
073    }
074    
075}
